  "payload": {
    "lesson": {
      "language": "zh-CN",
      "title": "椭圆过焦点的弦长范围",
      "problem": "<p class='font-medium text-slate-800'>【题目】</p><p>椭圆 $C:\\dfrac{x^2}{4}+\\dfrac{y^2}{3}=1$，过右焦点 $F(1,0)$ 的直线 $l$ 交 $C$ 于 $A,B$。求弦长 $|AB|$ 的取值范围。</p>",
      "answerLabel": "焦点弦长取值范围",
      "answer": "$|AB|\\in[3,\\ 4]$"
    },
    "steps": [
      {
        "title": "联立 + 韦达定理",
        "content": "<p>设 $l:\\,x=my+1$，代入椭圆得 $ 3 m^{2} + 4y^2+6 my-9=0 $，</p><p>$y_1+y_2=- \\frac{6 m}{3 m^{2} + 4},\\ y_1y_2=- \\frac{9}{3 m^{2} + 4}$。</p>"
      },
      {
        "title": "弦长公式",
        "content": "<p>$|AB|^2=(1+m^2)\\left[(y_1+y_2)^2-4y_1y_2\\right]=\\frac{144 \\left(m^{2} + 1\\right)^{2}}{\\left(3 m^{2} + 4\\right)^{2}}$。</p><p>令 $u=m^2\\ge0$：$|AB|^2=\\dfrac{144(u+1)}{(3u+4)^2}$，关于 $u$ 单调，$u=0$（竖直·通径）得最小 $9$，$u\\to\\infty$（水平·长轴）得最大 $16$。</p><div class='text-center py-3 bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-100 rounded-xl text-emerald-900 font-bold'>$$ |AB|\\in [3,\\ 4] $$</div>"
      }
    ],
